@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@username = admin
@password = admin123

### Login first
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{username}}&password={{password}}

### Deposit
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/account/600/deposit
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

amount=5000&description=Salary deposit

### Withdraw
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/account/604/withdraw
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

amount=1000&description=ATM withdrawal

### Transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/account/604/transfer
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

to_account=601&amount=2000&description=Rent payment

### View Statement
GET {{baseUrl}}/bank/account/604/statement

### View Statement with Date Range
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/account/604/statement
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

start_date=2025-01-01&end_date=2025-02-12